  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale-data variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed. Decision is Accepted pending planned re-validation against updated boundary-condition datasets; re-validation is scheduled but not yet completed.",
